#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:5334
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_COMBAT_HACK_FLEET_OUTCOME_NEUTRAL\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue to the fight!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:5339
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_COMBAT_HACK_FLEET_OUTCOME_BAD\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"This hack went terribly wrong, and their comms countered by giving away our "
"location!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:5342
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_COMBAT_HACK_FLEET_OUTCOME_BAD\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue to the fight!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:5347
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_COMBAT_HACK_FLEET_OUTCOME_BOSS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"This hack should have delayed the fleet a lot, but the effect was weaker than expected...\n"
"\t\t\n"
"\t\tSomeone interfered, and sent us strange coordinates with this attached: \"N00bs!!1!\"."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:5354
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_COMBAT_HACK_FLEET_OUTCOME_BOSS\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Weird, but we'll deal with that later. Continue to the fight!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:5384
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_HACK_FLEET_BOSS\"]/beaconType/unvisitedTooltip"
msgstr ""
"Someone dangerous enough to stop a strong RK Enigmashin hack dares you to "
"come!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:5387
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_HACK_FLEET_BOSS\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"A very mean-looking elite rebel ship is here. Its captain is staring you down, with just a hint of a spark in the eye.\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\"When I heard someone was playing games big time with the fleet's comms, I knew I had to meet the fools! And here you are, noobs!\n"
"\t\tI hope you don't mind that I'm calling you that, noobs. There's no harm in telling you that we all even respect the gumption, pissing off the largest army this side of the universe, that blankets entire sectors in the shadow of fleet ships.\n"
"\t\tBut me and my friends here didn't become MFKs by going all soft for that much, as one would guess.\n"
"\n"
"\t\tSo as a show of friendly rivalry, let me show you how it's done! Right before we murder you.\""

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:5398
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_HACK_FLEET_BOSS\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "A challenge, then? Let's go!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:5400
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_HACK_FLEET_BOSS\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"The vicious smile on the enemy captain's face widens. \"Nyahaha, Here's a taste!\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\t\tYou immediately notice malfunctions in many of your ship's systems! They must be using a combat augment! You probably expected that a hacker ship wouldn't play fair, but if you didn't, it's high time to consider a quick escape before something [style[color:ff3377]]worse[[/style]] happens."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:5415
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_HACK_FLEET_BOSS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:5420
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_HACK_FLEET_BOSS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"ANTI_VIRUS\"]/text"
msgstr "(Anti-Virus) Restore your systems."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:5422
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_HACK_FLEET_BOSS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"ANTI_VIRUS\"]/event/text"
msgstr "Your systems are restored to full power."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:5432
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_HACK_FLEET_BOSS\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"ANTI_VIRUS\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:5441
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//event[@name=\"RK_HACK_FLEET_BOSS\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"We have learned our lesson, we beg you to let us go! Here's tribute for you "
"and the Rebellion as proof."

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:5453
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RK_HACK_FLEET_BOSS\"]/surrender/text"
msgstr ""
"\"Playing tough huh! How do you like this?\"\n"
"\n"
"\t\t\tStronger malfunctions affect even more of your ship's systems!"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:5492
msgid ""
"data/events_special_storage.xml.append$//ship[@name=\"SHIP_RK_HACK_FLEET_BOSS\"]/surrender/choice[1]/text"
