msgstr ""
"As you finish scavenging, you find very peculiar equipment!\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tAnalyzing the wreck, you understand that an internal apparatus can let you extract something from the ship, but then everything will blow up.\n"
"\t\t\t\t\tWhat do you pick?"

