" and @lvl=\"1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"RK Scorch \"Hellion Wraps\": In fire, your crew have 1.75x movement and "
"sabotage speed, and deal 1.75x combat and door damage, on both ships. "
"[ALREADY INSTALLED]"

#: src-en/data/events_special_storage.xml.append:7050
msgid ""
